    "biography": {
      "value": "<p>The earth-wight of the Singing Islands, an ancient geothermal spirit corrupted by the Rot. Once a guardian that tended the volcanic vents warming the island gardens, now a territorial destroyer that cannot distinguish pilgrim from threat. Its stone-and-root body leaves craters with every step. Deep within, the original spirit screams -- trapped, unable to stop or die cleanly until freed or defeated.</p>",
